Late AmaZulu Regen,  Queen Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu’s memorial service is being held at the Kwakhangela Palace in northern Kwazulu-Natal,  following her internment in a private ceremony. Below is the live stream: The KwaZulu-Natal government says extra care is being taken against the possible spread of COVID-19 at the memorial service for AmaZulu regent -Queen Mantfombi* Dlamini Zulu. The Queen was interred at the crack of dawn on Thursday.